According to a report by Intel Market Research, the global Coconut Market was valued at USD 14,199 million in 2024 and is projected to grow from USD 15,320 million in 2025 to USD 24,045 million by 2032, registering a CAGR of 8.0% during the forecast period.
The global coconut market is witnessing strong growth as consumers increasingly seek natural, plant-based, and functional products across food & beverages, cosmetics, healthcare, and personal care industries. Coconut-derived products—including coconut water, coconut milk, coconut oil, desiccated coconut, snacks, and coconut fiber—continue to gain popularity due to their nutritional benefits, versatility, and expanding application base.
